        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/li-j>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/li-z>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/liang-l>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/lin-h>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/ma-j>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/wang-j>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/wang-x>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/wang-y>,
        <https://w3id.org/pyeuropepmc/author/xu-y>,
